<BaseHead />
<Header />

<main class="container" style="max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;">
  <marquee behavior="scroll" direction="left" scrollamount="3" style="background-color: #003366; color: white; padding: 5px; font-size: 13px;">
    Quarterly Productivity Reports Show Historic Stability · Public Conduct Handbook Updated · New Compliance Monitors Installed in Sector 7 · Sector 12 Announces Record Attendance at Morale Rally · All Associates Reminded to Carry ID Badges at All Times
  </marquee>

  <h2 style="border-bottom: 2px solid #003366; color: #003366; margin-top: 20px;">EctoCorp Newswire</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 12px; color: gray; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    Official bulletins from the Broadcast & Messaging Bureau · December 31, 1999∞
  </p>

  <article style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
    <h3 style="margin: 0; color: #003366;">Quarterly Productivity Reports Show Historic Stability</h3>
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;">Filed: 1999∞.6 · Staff Writer: P. Aldridge</p>
    <p>
      EctoCorp has announced an unprecedented sixth consecutive quarter of stability across all sectors.
      Human Resources praised all associates for their continued loyalty and output. Compliance Enforcement Division
      credited “consistent vigilance” as a key factor in this achievement.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
    <h3 style="margin: 0; color: #003366;">Public Conduct Handbook Updated</h3>
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;">Filed: 1999∞.5 · Staff Writer: R. Klemens</p>
    <p>
      Human Resources has issued the 1999∞ Public Conduct Handbook revision. Associates are advised to review the
      updates, particularly Section 4 — Interactions with Enforcement. Copies are available at all sector bulletin
      boards and via intranet download.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
    <h3 style="margin: 0; color: #003366;">New Compliance Monitors Installed in Sector 7</h3>
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;">Filed: 1999∞.5 · Staff Writer: L. Donnelly</p>
    <p>
      The Compliance Enforcement Division has completed installation of upgraded monitors in Sector 7 to ensure
      prompt reporting and efficient resolution of any irregularities. Associates should familiarize themselves
      with the new interface and report technical issues immediately.
    </p>
  </article>

  <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;">

  <p style="font-size: 11px; color: gray; text-align: center;">
    EctoCorp Broadcast & Messaging Bureau · All bulletins approved for public distribution.<br>
    Unauthorized duplication or alteration is a Class-3 Violation.
  </p>
</main>

<Footer />
